{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","bgm":"bgm01_anime03","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301001,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":800700,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"blackFrame"},{"chara":[{"id":800700}],"nameLeft":"Ria","nameRight":"","textRight":"You got a contract offer.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","turnEffect":"thinking"},{"chara":[{"id":800700}],"textRight":"They want you for the grand finale of@their upcoming fashion show."},{"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301001,"motion":400}],"textLeft":"[chara:301001:effect_emotion_surprise_0][se:7226_shock]What?! They want me to be the final model@onstage?"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_21101.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":301001,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"id":301001,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Ria","nameRight":"","textCenter":"(My turn's coming up.)","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","turnEffect":"blackPromist"},{"textRight":"Places, everyone!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301001}],"textCenter":"Got it!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":301001,"lipSynch":0,"motion":400}],"textCenter":"(Time to get going.)"},{"bg":"black","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301001,"motion":0}],"nameNarration":"","narration":"*Zap*","narrationBg":"black","narrationEffect":"in"},{"chara":[{"id":301001}],"narrationEffect":"out","textCenter":"[chara:301001:effect_emotion_surprise_0][se:7226_shock]What?! What's going on?!"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story10","textBg":"shout","textRight":"The lights are out! Hurry, get them back on!"},{"nameLeft":"","nameRight":"","textLeft":"What happened? A power outage?","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"textRight":"What? You sure it's not just part of the@show?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301001,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"textCenter":"(A power outage NOW?! Of course, right@when I'm about to take the stage...ugh!)","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":301001,"lipSynch":0,"motion":200}],"textCenter":"(My big chance! This is going to ruin@everything!)"},{"textBg":"shout","textRight":"The lights are back on!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301001,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0}],"textCenter":"(Phew!)"},{"textLeft":"Ah, but it looks like the audience lost@interest due to the power outage."},{"textLeft":"If we can't get their attention back, it@might be better to just end it here."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301001}],"textCenter":"What?!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":301001,"lipSynch":0,"motion":200}],"textCenter":"(You have got to be kidding! Cancel the@show now?!)"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"slideOutLeftFast","id":301001}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"effect":"slideInRightFast","face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":301001,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":800700,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"","nameRight":"Ria","textBg":"shout","textRight":"Please, wait!"},{"chara":[{"id":301001}],"textRight":"I'll win them back somehow."},{"chara":[{"id":800700}],"textLeft":"But..."},{"chara":[{"id":301001,"motion":400}],"textRight":"Please let me try!"},{"bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":800700}],"textLeft":"Very well. I believe in you, Miss Ami."},{"bg":"bg_adv_15022.jpg","bgm":"bgm03_story07","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":800100,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":800300,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameLeft":"","nameRight":"","textLeft":"The last girl looked pretty nice, I guess...","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":800300}],"textRight":"Yeah, but I didn't enjoy myself as much as@at other shows."},{"chara":[{"id":800100}],"textLeft":"It could have been great if it was part of@the show, not a blackout."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":800300}],"textRight":"True, true! It just turned out to be a@regular old power outage, huh?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301001,"lipSynch":0,"motion":300,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Ria","textCenter":"...","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"bg":"bg_adv_21071.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":2,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":301001,"motion":0}],"nameNarration":"Ria","narration":"If only the power hadn't gone out!","narrationBg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","narrationEffect":"in","turnEffect":"stop"},{"narration":"I would've been swamped with admirers@from countless fashion magazines!"},{"narration":"No...that's not quite right."},{"narration":"I'm the one who was at fault. I wasn't@able to overcome the power outage."},{"narration":"Even so..."},{"chara":[{"id":301001,"motion":200}],"narrationEffect":"out","textBg":"shout","textCenter":"I can't get over how disappointed I am!!!"},{"bgm":"stop","nameRight":"Ria's Mother","textBg":"shout","textRight":"Ria! Will you stop making so much noise up@there every single morning?! Pipe down!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301001,"motion":0}],"textCenter":"[chara:301001:effect_emotion_surprise_0][se:7226_shock]Wait, it's a dream!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301001,"motion":300}],"textCenter":"I've been dreaming about this every night@because I'm so nervous about it."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":301001}],"textCenter":"But they were just dreams. I, Ria Ami, will@make the show a success!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301001,"motion":100}],"textCenter":"Ah ha ha ha ha haaa!"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}